<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 30, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 10; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
