(3-0), the second-ranked JC team in the nation. At 7:30 p.m. Loyola (3-0), the 
eighth-ranked high school team in the state, plays host to Antelope Valley 
(2-1). Antelope Valley posted consecutive shutouts before losing to 
third-ranked Bakersfield, 35-13, last week. 
</P>
<P>
 Monday, 3:30 p.m., at the Valley College pool: Harvard-Westlake and Notre 
