<TEXT>
<P>
 More than 1,000 Harley-Davidson motorcycle enthusiasts from throughout 
Southern California are expected to join a fund-raiser today to benefit a local 
homeless shelter, an event spokeswoman has announced. 
</P>
<P>
 Called "Harleys for the Homeless," the event will consist of a ride from Santa 
