 Paul Kariya: 9 
</P>
<P>
 Age: 19 
</P>
<P>
 Left wing 
</P>
<P>
 Shoots: L 
</P>
<P>
 Hasn't played a game yet, but he's already the most celebrated Duck in the 
team's short history. Turns 20 Oct. 16. Expected to add tremendous offensive 
skills to the team. Led Canada to the silver medal in the 1994 Olympics and to 
the gold at the '94 World Championships. 
</P>
