<DOCNO> LA093094-0309 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 084318 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 30, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Special Section; Part V; Page 8; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
